data.text:
Ducks move local broadcasts to over-air channel, streaming

The Ducks announced on Tuesday that 65 games next season will be on an over-the-air channel in Los Angeles.

Diamond drops Mavs, Pels but agrees to air NBA, NHL in 2024-25

Diamond Sports Group, the bankrupt operator of Bally Sports channels, has reached new deals with the NBA and NHL and has ensured that it will broadcast games for teams under its portfolio at least through the upcoming 2024-25 seasons.

NHL trade grades: Askarov addition accelerates Sharks' build

No. 1 pick Macklin Celebrini will have the top goalie prospect in hockey behind him; has the timeline been moved up? Here are our grades for both GMs.

Keanu Reeves signs one-day contract with Windsor Spitfires

Keanu Reeves' autographed jersey from his ceremonial one-day stint with the team will be auctioned off for charity.
